column5: Five guys here have asked/PM'd/e-mailed about having their boats fixed, in the last 2 weeks.  Only one of the five has bothered to respond to my email, in regards to what it would take to fix their boat.  My shop is booking up fast(er than I'd like) so if you wanna snooze... you'ze is gonna lose!   Wayne
Funny 4 out of 5 guys have dropped in here to have their boats fixed and they all picked up their bonus  girly calendars   I was wondering where the other guy went
